---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="CI/CD Pipeline Automation | Banu Priya" description="Production-grade GitLab CI/CD pipeline with multi-stage builds, Docker optimization, SAST/DAST security scanning, and blue-green deployments.">
  <Navbar />
  <main style="padding-top:80px;min-height:100vh;">
    <div style="padding:4rem 1.5rem 2rem;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(15,22,41,0.9) 0%,transparent 100%);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(30,45,74,0.4);">
      <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
        <a href="/#projects" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.35rem;font-size:0.82rem;color:rgba(100,116,139,0.7);text-decoration:none;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">вҶҗ Back to Projects</a>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:1rem;">
          {['GitLab CI','Docker','SAST','Blue-Green'].map(tag => (
            <span style="display:inline-flex;padding:0.2rem 0.7rem;background:rgba(252,109,38,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(252,109,38,0.25);border-radius:4px;font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;color:#FC6D26;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;">{tag}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
        <h1 style="font-size:clamp(1.75rem,5vw,2.75rem);font-weight:900;color:white;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">CI/CD Pipeline <span style="color:#FC6D26;">Automation</span></h1>
        <p style="color:rgba(148,163,184,0.85);font-size:1rem;line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Full-featured GitLab CI/CD pipeline achieving zero-downtime deployments with built-in security scanning and instant rollback capability.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/priyapbanu/cicd-pipeline-automation" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary" style="font-size:0.85rem;padding:0.6rem 1.25rem;">View on GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem 6rem;" class="prose-devops">
      <h2>Pipeline Stages</h2>
      <div style="background:#0d1117;border:1px solid rgba(30,45,74,0.8);border-radius:12px;padding:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;overflow-x:auto;">
        <pre style="color:#34d399;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.78rem;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">{`
в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
в”Ӯ  Build   в”ӮвҶ’ в”Ӯ  Test    в”ӮвҶ’ в”Ӯ Security в”ӮвҶ’ в”Ӯ  Deploy  в”ӮвҶ’ в”Ӯ Cleanup  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ          в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ          в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ          в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  Green   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ Docker   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ Unit     в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ SAST     в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ Smoke    в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ Scale    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ Build    в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ Tests    в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ DAST     в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ Tests    в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ Down Old в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ & Push   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ Coverage в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ Trivy    в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ Switch   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ Slot     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ          в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ          в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ Scan     в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ Traffic  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ          в”Ӯ
в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ  в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
  ~3 mins       ~5 mins       ~4 mins        ~7 mins        ~1 min
`}</pre>
      </div>

      <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:0.75rem;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        {['GitLab CI/CD','Docker 24 + BuildKit','Docker Registry','Trivy Scanner','SonarQube','pytest + coverage','Kubernetes','Helm','Slack Notifications','AWS ECR'].map(item => (
          <div style="padding:0.6rem 0.85rem;background:rgba(21,29,53,0.8);border:1px solid rgba(252,109,38,0.2);border-radius:8px;font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:600;color:rgba(226,232,240,0.85);">{item}</div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <h2>Folder Structure</h2>
      <div style="background:#0d1117;border:1px solid rgba(30,45,74,0.8);border-radius:12px;padding:1.5rem;margin-bottom:2rem;overflow-x:auto;">
        <pre style="color:#e2e8f0;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.8rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">{`cicd-pipeline-automation/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ .gitlab-ci.yml             # Main pipeline definition
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Dockerfile                 # Multi-stage optimized build
в”ңв”Җв”Җ .dockerignore
в”ңв”Җв”Җ pipeline/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ templates/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ build.gitlab-ci.yml
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ test.gitlab-ci.yml
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ security.gitlab-ci.yml
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ deploy.gitlab-ci.yml
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ scripts/
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ blue-green-deploy.sh
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ smoke-test.sh
в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ notify-slack.sh
в”ңв”Җв”Җ kubernetes/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ deployment-blue.yaml
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ deployment-green.yaml
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ service.yaml
в”ңв”Җв”Җ sonar-project.properties   # SonarQube config
в””в”Җв”Җ tests/
    в”ңв”Җв”Җ unit/
    в””в”Җв”Җ integration/`}</pre>
      </div>

      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;">
        {[
          'вҡЎ Docker BuildKit for 60% faster image builds with caching',
          'рҹ§Ә Unit tests with coverage gates (min 80% required)',
          'рҹ”Қ SonarQube static analysis with quality gate enforcement',
          'рҹӣЎпёҸ Trivy container scanning вҖ” blocks on HIGH/CRITICAL CVEs',
          'рҹҹў Blue-green deployment with smoke test validation',
          'вҸӘ Instant rollback вҖ” single kubectl patch command',
          'рҹ”” Slack notifications on pipeline success/failure',
          'рҹ“Ұ Artifacts with Docker image SBOMs for compliance',
        ].map(f => (
          <li style="padding:0.6rem 1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;background:rgba(21,29,53,0.5);border:1px solid rgba(252,109,38,0.15);border-radius:8px;font-size:0.875rem;color:rgba(148,163,184,0.85);">{f}</li>
        ))}
      </ul>

      <div style="margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <a href="https://github.com/priyapbanu/cicd-pipeline-automation" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">View Full Source on GitHub вҶ’</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
